	<h1 class="title">据说，人们越来越爱吃酸酸的东西了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/112316/small/112316.JPG?1442220004" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">罗芊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-20 07:30:01 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19187/medium/19187.jpg?1450245341" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19187" data-title="《据说，人们越来越爱吃酸酸的东西了？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19187/medium/19187.jpg?1450245341" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19187.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
